### Update existing fuel data with invalid JSON body
PUT http://localhost:8090/fuelData/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": null,
  "make": "",
  "model": "Civic",
  "vehicleClass": "Sedan"
}

### Delete fuel data by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8090/fuelData/1